item.title: Trip to Seattle
item.description: Just wrapped up visiting a few friends and checking out the city of Seattle for the first time. Here are some photos I took from across the city this weekend. Scenery View of Seattle from Kerry Park. The same view of Seattle from Kerry Park, taken at night. The Olympic Mountains as seen from Queen Anne. The Seattle Great Wheel. Pike Place Market. Intersection of Western Ave and Virginia St.
